nk I'm ready to trust humans again. \"/speak {{ModId}}_Marigold \"Because of you. $h \"/emote farmer 20/pause 1000/speak {{ModId}}_Marigold \"That's.. that's what I wanted to say. \"/speak {{ModId}}_Marigold \"Thank you @ $h\"/end"
